## Hypoxic-ischemic encephalopathy (HIE)

::: columns
::: column
 
- Umbrella term for perinatal brain injury
- Present as encephalopathic newborns, +/- seizures
- Patterns of injury due to HIE depened on *timing* and *degree* of ischemia
::: 

